  ],
  "remarks": "OJSC “EHMZ named after N. D. Zelinsky” is a Russian manufacturer of filter-type personal and collective protective equipment, including for the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation and other Russian government institutions. In addition, the company produces filters for tanks, armoured vehicles and military aircraft, used by the Russian military. OJSC “EHMZ named after N. D. Zelinsky” is therefore supporting materially the Government of the Russian Federation, which is responsible for the annexation of Crimea and the destabilisation of Ukraine.",
